feat: add standalone MCP server for bridge tools (hr-eq8.5)

Create cmd/herald-bridges-mcp, a self-contained MCP server binary that
exposes comms and health bridge tools via the MCP stdio protocol. Uses
direct HTTP calls to myndy-comms and myndy-health services (no dependency
on herald-private module). Implements JSON-RPC 2.0 MCP server protocol
(initialize, tools/list, tools/call). Includes 9 tests and README docs.

